Tom Gulager https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tom_Gulager 0 Tom Christian Gulager (born July 21, 1965) is an American actor. He is the son of actors Clu Gulager and Miriam Byrd-Nethery and brother of actor/director John Gulager. He is best known for his roles in his brother's film series Feast.
